Package backEnd

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    EventInfo
    Contains all of the information about the generic case of a random event
    Game
    Where the game happens
    Island
    Island is either home or destination for a ship.
    Item
    Items that are available to buy or sell by the player from/to a store when visiting the island
    Items includes food and weapons
    MapRoute
    Finds routes between 2 islands and the map of them
    Pirates
    A type of the random events player may meet while sailing
    Player
    A player is the captain of the game
    RandomEvent
    Super class of random events that can happen during a sail
    RescueSailors
    A type of the random events player may meet while sailing
    Route
    The path that the player can take from the island they are based to another island
    There are 2 different routes connecting each pair of islands, in total there are 20 routes in the game
    Ship
    Ship is the vehicle to travel from an island to the other
    There are 4 ships for player to choose from
    Store
    Store is a place to trade good for player
    There are 5 stores in total, each is situated in a unique island
    Weapon
    This is a sub class of Item class, a type of item
    Weather
    A type of the random events player may meet while sailing
